message.body: Hey! Brandon and I are going to leave Harrisburg in about 45 minutes. What time will you guys be partying til?
If we show up around 9:15 is that cool??
Totally!!! We will be here! Yay!!!

Thanks for coming out last night!! It was great hanging with you. I love the photo you took of Drew and I. If you still have it, will you send me the photo via email? Let me know if you need help creating flames for your video w/ Hunter. I'm happy to let you use my AE plugin.
